<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
    PockPock mascot icon foreground — 108 × 108 dp adaptive-icon foreground.
    Viewport: 512 × 512.  Chicken center: (256, 285).  Radius: 100.

    Colors match ChickenSkin cold (low-player) theme:
      #9dd4f5  lowPlayerLight  — body fill / wing primary / feather primary
      #52b6f2  lowPlayerDark   — stroke / iris / beak / wing secondary / feather secondary

    Layer order (back → front):
      Wings (secondary then primary, before body so body clips the root)
      Body fill + stroke ring
      Head feathers (on top of body)
      Eyes (sclera, iris, pupil, highlight)
      Beak

    Eye iris offset: down-right (~45°), giving irisShift ≈ (+8, +8) from eye centre.
-->
